article_title: Obamacare Was Supposed To Kill Medicare Advantage. It Only Made It Stronger.

article_metadata.description: Marilyn Tavenner is about to make an unprecedented move: From head of Medicare, to the nation's top lobbyist for private insurers. And one of her top priorities? Fighting to protect Medicare Advantage.
article_metadata.author: Dan Diamond
